open notepad 
copy and paste the code of your desired game
save txt file 
open browser
type txt to html converter or open this link (https://cloudconvert.com/txt-to-html)
convert txt files to html 
download them 
press on the html file and browser should open
if you want to change the browser it uses then change your default browser to the one you want 

